---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/MiFoto.png";
---


<!-- Main container -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row "
>
  <!-- Image -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MiFoto.src}
      alt="Photo of Lautaro"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Text -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Lautaro</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I am from <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Argentina</span> and I
      currently work as a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >full-stack software developer</span
      >, with a focus on
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >front-end development</span
      >
      and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">user experience</span>,
      using technologies such as
      <span class="text-primary italic"
        >React, Astro, JavaScript, TypeScript, Bootstrap, Tailwind, CSS,
        Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB and MySQL</span
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      My interest in
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">technology</span> and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">programming</span> began while I
      was studying for a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >University Technical Degree in Automation</span
      >
      at
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">UnCuyo</span>. In the
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">computer science</span>
      class, I had my first contact with the world of programming. Motivated by
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">curiosity</span>, I continued
      studying in a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">self-taught</span> way, then in a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >technical degree focused on software development</span
      >, and I decided that this was what I wanted to do at a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">professional</span> level.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I am always committed to
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >continuous growth</span
      >
      and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">improvement</span> in my skills,
      seeking to adapt to new
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">technological advances</span> and
      to improve myself at a
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">professional</span> and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">personal</span> level.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
